@page "/sme-questionnaire/privacy"
@rendermode InteractiveServer
@attribute [AllowAnonymous]

<PageTitle>Privacy Notice</PageTitle>

<h1>Privacy Notice</h1>

<p>This notice explains how SME questionnaire data is collected and used.</p>

<h2>What data we collect</h2>
<p>We collect profile, skills, equipment, software, and questionnaire response data that you provide.</p>

<h2>Why we collect it</h2>
<p>We use this information for curriculum development and planning.</p>

<h2>Who can access it</h2>
<p>Access is limited to authorized staff.</p>

<h2>Retention</h2>
<p>We retain questionnaire data only as long as needed for curriculum and planning purposes.</p>

<h2>Security</h2>
<p>We apply reasonable safeguards to protect stored data.</p>

<h2>Personal information</h2>
<p><strong>We do not sell your personal information.</strong></p>

<h2>Questions or removal requests</h2>
<p>Contact the InsTK team using your standard program support channel.</p>
